  <summary date="2017-06-10T16:33:04Z" status="Introduced in House">Atomic Veterans Service Medal Act 

This bill directs the Department of Defense (DOD) to design and produce an Atomic Veterans Service Medal to honor retired and former members of the Armed Forces who are radiation-exposed veterans.

DOD may provide for issuance of the Medal to the next-of-kin of a deceased radiation-exposed veteran.</summary>
